text.autoconfig.repurposed_structures-ma: Add the ID/resource location of the biome you don't want
RS's dungeons to spawn in. Separate each ID with a comma ,
Example: "minecraft:ice_spikes,awesome_mod:awesome_biome"
Blacklisted Dungeon Biomes
Add the ID/resource location of the biome you don't want
RS's swamp trees to spawn in. Separate each ID with a comma ,
Example: "minecraft:ice_spikes,awesome_mod:awesome_biome"
